### =========================================
### HJK 手表 API 测试文件
### 设备 ID: 359339078150060
### 基础地址: http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk
### =========================================

### ========================
### 1. 下发指令类
### ========================

### 1.1 远程立即定位 (command=128)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=128

### 1.2 远程测量心率 (command=127)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=127

### 1.3 远程关机 (command=121)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=121

### 1.4 远程测量血压 (command=120)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=120

### 1.5 远程测量体温 (command=117)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=117

### 1.6 远程测量血氧 (command=119)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=119

### 1.7 远程设备重启 (command=141)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=141

### 1.8 恢复出厂设置 (command=90)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=90

### 1.9 查找设备 (command=164)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=164

### 1.10 远程开始测量血糖 (command=162)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=162

### ========================
### 2. 带参数指令类
### ========================

### 2.1 下发文字信息到手表 (command=115, cmdvalue=hello)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=115&cmdvalue=hello

### 2.2 下发二维码信息到手表 (command=142, cmdvalue=1234567890)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=142&cmdvalue=1234567890

### 2.3 设置计步器工作时间 (command=143, cmdvalue=09:00-21:00)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=143&cmdvalue=09:00-21:00

### 2.4 设置睡眠时间 (command=147, cmdvalue=21:00-08:00)
### 21:00 是睡眠时间，08:00 是起床时间
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=147&cmdvalue=21:00-08:00

### 2.5 设置免打扰时间 (command=140, cmdvalue=21:10-7:30-1)
### 最多设置4组，最少1组；-0关闭 -1开启
### 示例: 21:10-7:30-1,21:10-7:30-0,21:10-7:30-0,21:10-7:30-1
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=140&cmdvalue=21:10-7:30-1,21:10-7:30-0,21:10-7:30-0,21:10-7:30-1

### 2.6 久坐提醒设置 (command=146, cmdvalue=1,30)
### 1=开启久坐, 0=关闭；30=间隔分钟(支持30/60/90)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=146&cmdvalue=1,30

### 2.7 设置测量健康偏差参数 (command=103, cmdvalue=5,6,5,10,1.2)
### 格式: 心率,高压,低压,血氧,体温
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=103&cmdvalue=5,6,5,10,1.2

### 2.8 下发血压学习后的值到手表 (command=152, cmdvalue=80,120)
### 80=舒张压, 120=收缩压
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=152&cmdvalue=80,120

### 2.9 下发血糖学习信息到手表 (command=161, cmdvalue=1,9.6)
### 1=血糖类型(0空腹/1餐后半小时/2餐后1h/3餐后2h/4餐后4h), 9.6=血糖值
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=161&cmdvalue=1,9.6

### 2.10 设置蓝牙扫描参数 (command=148, cmdvalue=1)
### cmdvalue=1 表示1分钟扫描一次蓝牙并上传
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=148&cmdvalue=1

### 2.11 设备快捷拨号 (command=163, cmdvalue=187772727772)
### cmdvalue=快捷拨号的号码
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&command=163&cmdvalue=187772727772

### ========================
### 3. 下发语音到手表 (POST - JSON)
### ========================

### 3.1 下发语音到手表 (command=118)
POST http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/submitcommand.htm
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceid": "359339078150060",
    "command": 118,
    "cmdvalue": "YmFzZTY05Yqo56CB55qE6K+d6Zmp5pWw5o2u" 
}

### ========================
### 4. 设备配置参数修改
### ========================

### 4.1 设置 SOS 联系人
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&sos1=13433333333&sos2=13444444444&sos3=134444444434

### 4.2 清除 SOS 联系人
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&sos1=+&sos2=+&sos3=+

### 4.3 设置定位上传间隔 (30分钟)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&locationtimeinterval=30

### 4.4 设置心率上传间隔和安全阀值
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&maxheartrate=100&minheartrate=60&heartratetimeinterval=30

### 4.5 设置血压上传安全阀值
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&bplowmin=50&bplowmax=90&bphighmin=100&bphighmax=150&bpi=30

### 4.6 设置血氧上传安全阀值
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&bloodoxmax=99&bloodoxmin=9

### 4.7 设置体温间隔 (清除)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&tpi=&oxi=

### 4.8 设置联系人号码
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&pbname1=5byg5Li95Y2O&book1=13528897740&pbname2=5byg5Zu96Imv&book2=13502863143&pbname3=6YKx5ben57qi&book3=13662562721

### 4.9 清除联系人号码
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&pbname1=+&book1=+

### 4.10 设置服务号码
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&num1=13411111111

### 4.11 设置血压学习值
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&studybloodp=80,120

### 4.12 设置喝水、吃药提醒时间
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&medicine1=0:0&m1=1&medicine2=0:0&m2=1&medicine3=0:0&m3=1

### 4.13 设置开关机时间
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&of_status=1&of_on=08:00&of_off=21:00

### 4.14 设置语音闹钟 (POST - JSON)
POST http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/setWatch.htm
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceid": "359339078150060",
    "reminds": [
        {
            "name": "起床闹钟",
            "time": "07:00",
            "status": 1,
            "audio": "5b2T6Zet5ZCO5b6X5L2g",
            "week": "1111111"
        }
    ]
}

### ========================
### 5. 电子围栏
### ========================

### 5.1 设置圆形电子围栏 (GET)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/updateelectricfence.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&longitude=112.415224&latitude=26.937528&fanwei=3000

### 5.2 取消圆形电子围栏 (fanwei=0)
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/updateelectricfence.htm?deviceid=359339078150060&longitude=112.415224&latitude=26.937528&fanwei=0

### 5.3 设置多边形电子围栏 (POST)
POST http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/updateelectricfence.htm
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceid": "359339078150060",
    "name": "公司围栏",
    "path": [
        {"lon": 113.223, "lat": 23.4445},
        {"lon": 113.323, "lat": 23.5445},
        {"lon": 113.423, "lat": 23.4445}
    ]
}

### 5.4 清除多边形电子围栏 (POST - path为空数组)
POST http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/updateelectricfence.htm
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "deviceid": "359339078150060",
    "name": "公司围栏",
    "path": []
}

### ========================
### 6. 服务 API
### ========================

### 6.1 查看设备长连接是否在线
GET http://yg.hxinwatch.com/sdkapi/api/push/hjk/getWatchOnlineStatus.htm?deviceid=359339078150060

